.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-FEE-BASE-SKEWNESS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-fee-base-skewness \- FEAT-2823 peer-fee-base-skewness
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-fee-base-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes skewness of fee_base_msat values across peer channels (FEAT-2823).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.TP
.B fee_base_skewness_peer
Fisher-Pearson skewness of fee_base_msat values per peer channel.
.TP
.B n
Number of data points used.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
